tool_description: Search Engine data at scale. Uses city-level geo-targeting via residential proxies for targeted queries. Extract data such as organic results, paid results, related questions, top stories, people also ask, pagination, etc. in JSON format
name: SERP
title: SERP

api_list.name: Search
api_list.description: This endpoint allows you to search Google based on some certain parameters

required_parameters.name: q
required_parameters.description: This is the search query as you'd have in a regular Google search. Learn more:  [https://moz.com/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-the-google-search-parameters](https://moz.com/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-the-google-search-parameters).

optional_parameters.name: hl
optional_parameters.description: Web interface language. Autodetected from the `domain` parameter if not supplied. Supported values are: [https://serptools.cyclic.app/google_languages](https://serptools.cyclic.app/google_languages)

optional_parameters.name: num
optional_parameters.description: Number of search results. Values can be 1 - 100

optional_parameters.name: proxy_location
optional_parameters.description: These are the supported locations. We offer city-level geotargeting, making it possible to narrow down your queries. See all the supported locations here: [https://serptools.cyclic.app/proxy_locations](https://serptools.cyclic.app/proxy_locations)

optional_parameters.name: domain
optional_parameters.description: Specify the type of Google domain to be used. This defaults to `google.com`. See all supported domains here: [https://serptools.cyclic.app/domains](https://serptools.cyclic.app/domains)

optional_parameters.name: device
optional_parameters.description: Specify the kind of device to be used for the search. This defaults to `desktop`

optional_parameters.name: include_html
optional_parameters.description: Include raw html in response. This is good for debugging. It defaults to false

optional_parameters.name: gl
optional_parameters.description: Country code. Autodetected from the `domain` parameter if not supplied. Supported values are: [https://serptools.cyclic.app/google_countries](https://serptools.cyclic.app/google_countries)

api_list.name: Status
api_list.description: Check service availability. We offer 99.999% SLA.
